A random generator (string and number) provided as a jQuery plugin

Usage is fairly simple. Set up a div you want to use to collect entropy.

Then simply call the plugin like this:

$(function() {
	$("#jqrg").jQrg({
		'rSize'  : '10' //size of the generated string
		'pool'   : 'abcdefghijlmnopqrstuvwxyz' //tell the plugin what characters to use to generate the string
		'target' : '#output' //the id of the target input field
	});
});

